text: Lara Fabian (born January 9, 1970) is a Belgian singer. She has sold more than twenty million records worldwide. She sings in French, Spanish, English and other languages. Fabian was born in Etterbeek, Brussels, Belgium to a Sicilian mother and Belgian father. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:People from Brussels-Capital Region Category:Canadian singers Category:Musicians from Brussels
